SURAT PAULUS KEPADA

THE EPISTLE OF PAUL

JEMAAT DI EFESUS

TO THE EPHESIANS

 

 

Penulis: Rasul Paulus (1:1).

Author: The apostle Paul (1:1).

 

 

Waktu Penulisan: Kira-kira 64 M.

Time of Writing: Approximately A.D. 64.

 

 

Tempat penulisan: Roma, tempat Paulus dipenjarakan (3:1; 4:1; 6:20; Kis. 28:30).

Place of Writing: Rome, where Paul was imprisoned (3:1; 4:1; 6:20; Acts 28:30).

 

 

Penerima: Orang-orang kudus di Efesus (1:1).

Recipients: The saints in Ephesus (1:1).

 

 

Pokok: Gereja - Rahasia Kristus, Tubuh Kristus sebagai Kepenuhan Kristus, menjadi Kepenuhan Allah

Subject of Ephesians: The ChurchThe Mystery of Christ, the Body of Christ as the Fullness of Christ, Becoming the Fullness of God
